trans-unit.source: Generates the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] on behalf of its host, such as an <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Genererar den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] för värden, t.ex en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: ItemContainerGenerator implements <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator>, which is the interface that defines a type which: - Maintains an association between the data view of a multiple-item control, such as <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ContainerFromElement%2A> and the corresponding <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> items.
trans-unit.target: ItemContainerGenerator implementerar <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator>, vilket är det gränssnitt som definierar en typ som:-upprätthåller en association mellan datavy för en kontroll med flera objekt, t.ex <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ContainerFromElement%2A>och motsvarande <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>objekt.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ContainerFromElement%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator>

trans-unit.source: - Generates <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> items on behalf of a multiple-item control.
trans-unit.target: -Genererar <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>objekt för en kontroll med flera objekt.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> type has a corresponding container type.
trans-unit.target: Varje <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>typen har en motsvarande behållartypen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: Container elements are the objects that contain the data items in the item collection.
trans-unit.target: Behållarelement är de objekt som innehåller dataobjekt i objektsamlingen.

trans-unit.source: For example, for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox>, the generated containers are <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBoxItem> controls; for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox>, they are <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBoxItem> controls.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox>, genererade behållare är <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBoxItem>styr; för <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox>, de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBoxItem>kontroller.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBoxItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ComboBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBoxItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> generates its items through the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator> interface.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>genererar element via den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator>gränssnitt.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemContainerGenerator%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> is of type ItemContainerGenerator, which implements the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator> interface.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemContainerGenerator%2A>egenskapen för den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>är av typen ItemContainerGenerator som implementerar det <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator>gränssnittet.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemContainerGenerator%2A>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you can access the ItemContainerGenerator object associated with your <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemContainerGenerator%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Därför kan du komma åt objektet ItemContainerGenerator som är associerade med din <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>med hjälp av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemContainerGenerator%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.ItemContainerGenerator%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you have a data-bound <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView>, and you want to get a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem> based on its index or its associated data item, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromItem%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Om du har en databunden exempelvis <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView>, och du vill hämta en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem>baserat på dess index eller dess associerade data, kan du använda den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromItem%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metod.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromItem%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView>

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.IndexFromContainer%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ItemFromContainer%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to get the index or data item associated with a given generated container element.
trans-unit.target: Du kan också använda den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.IndexFromContainer%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ItemFromContainer%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metod för att hämta objektet index eller data som associeras med en given genererade behållare element.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ItemFromContainer%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.IndexFromContainer%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Apart from those usages, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator> interface is used in advanced scenarios.
trans-unit.target: Förutom dessa användningsområden i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator>gränssnitt används i scenarion med avancerad.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator>

trans-unit.source: Typically, advanced applications that have their own implementation of a virtualizing panel call members of the interface.
trans-unit.target: Avancerade program som har sina egna implementering av en virtualisering panel anropa vanligtvis medlemmar i gränssnittet.
